Summary: Automated Usenet Client
Name: lottanzb
Version: 0.6
Release: 8.1
Source0: https://launchpad.net/lottanzb/0.6/%{version}/+download/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
License: GPL
Group: Networking/News
BuildArch: noarch
BuildRequires: python2-devel
BuildRequires: intltool
Requires: python-kiwi
Requires: python2
Requires: hellanzb
Requires: pygtk2
Requires: pygtk2-libglade
URL: https://www.lottanzb.org/

%description
LottaNZB is a Usenet client that automates the download of Usenet files with
the help of NZB files. It uses HellaNZB as its backend and PyGTK for its user
interface.

%prep
%setup -q

%build
python2 setup.py build

